
OSX INSTALLATION
================

* Ensure you've got XCode installed

* Install the "brew" package manager from http://brew.sh/

* Use brew to install C++ dependencies

        brew install protobuf log4cpp snappy 

* Use easy_install to install Python dependencies

        sudo easy_install protobuf python-snappy

* Compile the software

        cd ztracer/src
        make

* You're ready to trace.

